    "description": "We at Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd are looking for an experienced Floor Manager based out of Agra. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nAsian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
